LDA 4201H    ; Get the most significant BCD digit (TENS)
RLC          ; Rotate left
RLC          ; Rotate left
RLC          ; Rotate left
RLC          ; Rotate left â†’ adjust digit to left nibble
ANI F0H      ; Make least significant BCD digit zero
MOV C, A     ; Store partial result in C
LDA 4200H    ; Get the lower BCD digit (UNITS)
ADD C        ; Add to partial result
STA 4300H    ; Store final packed BCD result
HLT          ; Terminate program

